				<td colspan="2"><span>Ok got this from Casters Realm.
<br />

<br />
Singing Mastery - It increases the effectiveness of all songs which are singing based, even exceeding their normal restrictions.
<br />

<br />
Instrument Mastery - This ability allows a Bard's Instrument Based spells to exceed their normal caps and be even more effective than is normally possible, even with an epic.
<br />

<br />
I'll be getting IM1 first since most of the songs I use are instrument songs.  I'm going to bounce back and forth between the two.  IM1 first then SM1 and so on.
<br />

<br />
<img src="http://www.kinyen.com/images/EQImages/litesaber.gif"></span></td>
